packages/actions/docs/type-aliases/EthFeeHistoryJsonRpcResponse.md:Defined in: [packages/actions/src/eth/EthJsonRpcResponse.ts:78](https://github.com/evmts/tevm-monorepo/blob/main/packages/actions/src/eth/EthJsonRpcResponse.ts#L78)

codex
I’ve got enough context to edit. The changes are limited to the transport internals and the deprecated JSON-RPC fetcher: normalize pre-parsed bodies, stop buffering oversized streams, preserve ids, enforce strict envelopes only in compatibility mode, pass through malformed batch elements as per-item errors, return adapter promises, and make the fetcher match its exported response type.
